Chelsea Noble https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chelsea_Noble 0 Chelsea Noble (born Nancy Mueller, December 4, 1964) is an American actress. She is known for her role as Kate McDonnell on the television sitcom Growing Pains (1989–1992). She is the wife of her Growing Pains co-star, Kirk Cameron, and the sister-in-law of Candace Cameron Bure. Chelsea_Noble ( born Nancy_Mueller , December_4_,_1964 ) is an_American_actress .
